1
00:01:52,229 --> 00:01:53,430
I just saw

2
00:01:53,430 --> 00:01:54,870
a figure flash by.

3
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:04,870
There's nothing here.

4
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:06,640
Commander,

5
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,600
you must have got that wrong.

6
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,470
If you don't trust me,

7
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:17,079
you can come and check for yourself.

8
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:21,090
Now that Lord Fei has already checked,

9
00:02:21,150 --> 00:02:22,880
there's no need to check again.

10
00:02:23,190 --> 00:02:24,680
Let's patrol elsewhere.

11
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,300
Thanks for your hard work.

12
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:29,430
Well,

13
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,030
Lord Fei,

14
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:33,590
it's so late.

15
00:02:33,590 --> 00:02:35,320
Why are you still in the palace?

16
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,380
Don't even mention it.

17
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,630
Although the marriage ceremony is over,

18
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:41,150
Consort Ling's consummation

19
00:02:41,150 --> 00:02:43,000
is also part of the royal etiquette.

20
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,630
As long as it's related to etiquette,

21
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:46,800
I, the newly appointed Minister of Rites,

22
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,150
have to supervise it personally.

23
00:02:48,150 --> 00:02:49,350
It's so troublesome.

24
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:52,620
Then, why are you in the Imperial Garden?

25
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,810
Didn't you know that

26
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:56,930
Lord Zhang also
entered the palace tonight?

27
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,800
His Majesty needs to
discuss something with him.

28
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:01,680
So, he asked me to wait for him here.

29
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:03,750
What Lord Fei says makes sense.

30
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,190
You've worked hard.

31
00:03:05,190 --> 00:03:07,080
We will patrol with greater caution

32
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,150
to protect His Majesty

33
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:09,560
Lord Zhang, and you.

34
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:10,840
Thank you.

35
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:13,710
Let's go.

36
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,630
The palace is heavily guarded.

37
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:28,470
If you barge in like this,

38
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:30,150
you might get caught.

39
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,240
So what?

40
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:34,150
I can deal with them myself.

41
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:36,280
If someone is killed in the palace,

42
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:38,240
security measures will be tightened.

43
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,750
At that time, it will be

44
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:41,560
more difficult for you to take action.

45
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,079
If you have any other tasks coming up,

46
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:44,210
you can just tell me.

47
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,710
Maybe I can help.

48
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,370
I've explored the palace pretty well.

49
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:49,630
But

50
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:51,240
I need the defense maps of
the Tianlang Pass

51
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,680
and the capital.

52
00:03:53,030 --> 00:03:54,430
I'll have to trouble Lord Fei for that.

53
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:57,430
The defense maps of
the Tianlang Pass and the capital?

54
00:03:58,280 --> 00:04:00,240
Do you think a civil official like me

55
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,370
can get hold of such military secrets?

56
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,190
Even if I can,

57
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:07,080
how can you send them back to Changmo?

58
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,520
After the grand ceremony,

59
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,840
the envoy for the marriage alliance
will arrive in the capital,

60
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,700
and the Hall Master will come too.

61
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,080
The Hall Master is coming in person?

62
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,610
Alright.

63
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,570
I'm leaving.

64
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:18,630
Remember to get me the defense maps.

65
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:32,560
Jin Xi,

66
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,810
you can leave first.

67
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,120
I will serve Her Highness.

68
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,800
Yes.

69
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:45,480
You slept alone last night?

70
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:49,070
Yesterday, Liu Chu was
called away by Lord Zhang,

71
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:51,000
and didn't come back.

72
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,190
I fell asleep by myself.

73
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,000
On the first night of the wedding,

74
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,530
he didn't

75
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:59,090
consummate the marriage with you?

76
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:06,160
Greetings, Your Highness.

77
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,430
Greetings, Your Highness.

78
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,000
Before His Majesty went to court,

79
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,870
he specifically ordered me

80
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:14,160
to come and see

81
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:16,000
how you slept.

82
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:19,070
These were also

83
00:05:19,070 --> 00:05:20,600
ordered by His Majesty last night

84
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,680
in the Imperial Study.

85
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,390
See.

86
00:05:22,510 --> 00:05:25,040
I brought it to you
first thing in the morning.

87
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:26,800
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

88
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:29,630
Then, when will His Majesty come?

89
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:30,830
Well,

90
00:05:30,830 --> 00:05:32,159
I don't know.

91
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,240
But I believe

92
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,480
after His Majesty finishes court,

93
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,800
he will come to see you.

94
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:38,920
I shall take my leave now.

95
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,450
Alright.

96
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:51,600
General Xiao.

97
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,270
Lord Fei.

98
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:55,270
After days of comparison and analysis,

99
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:56,950
we found the plague in Huangpi Village

100
00:05:56,950 --> 00:05:58,430
indeed bears a striking resemblance

101
00:05:58,430 --> 00:06:00,240
to the great plague eight years ago.

102
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,440
They are just similar

103
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,630
but not the same?

104
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:03,240
No.

105
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:04,510
Although this disease

106
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:05,800
is very similar to

107
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,800
the great plague eight years ago,

108
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,510
we still found some

109
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:09,710
subtle differences.

110
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:12,480
Please look at the examination report,
My Lords.

111
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,870
An unknown toxin was found

112
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:16,800
in this plague.

113
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,680
I haven't found out

114
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:20,040
what exactly the poison is yet.

115
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,630
Poison?

116
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:22,120
Yes.

117
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,680
That is to say,

118
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:24,950
this epidemic

119
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,240
is not a natural disaster.

120
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,570
Not a natural disaster?

121
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:29,270
Could it be man-made?

122
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:32,480
You mean someone spread the poison?

123
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,750
We will find

124
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:35,159
the source of the ash as soon as possible

125
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:37,090
to help Lord Fei uncover the truth.

126
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:38,600
Thank you for your help.

127
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,950
Jin Xi.

128
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:47,000
It's so late.

129
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:49,390
Do you think Liu Chu is still coming?

130
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:55,560
No emperor visits a concubine's palace
every day.

131
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:57,250
If he doesn't come,

132
00:06:57,270 --> 00:06:58,750
we'll just rest early.

133
00:07:00,950 --> 00:07:01,750
Alright.

134
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,680
I'm sleepy anyway.

135
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:11,430
Greetings, Your Majesty.

136
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:13,690
Your Majesty, it's so late. You still...

137
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:16,830
I was just discussing with
Zhang Ruizhong and Li Shichang

138
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:19,070
about the expansion of the army
in the capital.

139
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:20,930
I came to you as soon as I finished.

140
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:22,730
Your Highness,

141
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:24,870
I'd better wait for you outside.

142
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:26,470
Call me if you need anything.

143
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,750
Who is this?

144
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,920
That's Jin Xi.

145
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,480
She accompanied me from Changmo

146
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,680
as my personal female official.

147
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,830
We grew up together.

148
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:46,070
For a moment just now,

149
00:07:48,070 --> 00:07:50,430
I felt like I had seen that look of hers

150
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,780
somewhere before.

151
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,310
You're familiar with her gaze?

152
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:53,950
Yeah.

153
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,480
It seems like

154
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:58,210
when Fei Zheng
entered the Prince's Mansion.

155
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,000
What are you talking about?

156
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,390
Lord Fei is a man.

157
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,800
Jin Xi is a girl.

158
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,830
How can they be the same?

159
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,430
Really, I'm not lying to you.

160
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:08,230
Forget it.

161
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:09,560
It's not important.

162
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,830
Tonight,

163
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:13,950
I will stay here with you.

164
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,240
Really?

165
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,160
Of course it is.

166
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,390
When have I ever lied to you?

167
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:18,830
Right?

168
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,680
Your Majesty.

169
00:08:24,070 --> 00:08:25,680
Your Majesty.

170
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:27,800
Damn Lord Zhang.

171
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,480
I

172
00:08:33,549 --> 00:08:34,750
will be right back.

173
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:38,299
You didn't come back
last time you said that.

174
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:42,909
I swear.

175
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,400
This is the last time.

176
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,480
It won't happen again.

177
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,080
All right.

178
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:47,030
Yeah.

179
00:08:47,550 --> 00:08:48,200
Okay.

180
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,150
Then,

181
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:49,970
I am leaving.

182
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:50,750
Okay.

183
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,480
Your Majesty.

184
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,200
Lord Zhang.

185
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,200
Okay.

186
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:03,910
Lord Zhang,

187
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:06,670
today isn't any special occasion.

188
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:08,000
Besides,

189
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,480
with so much wine,

190
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,140
how can the two of us finish it?

191
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:13,630
You may not know this, Your Majesty.

192
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:16,440
Today is the anniversary of

193
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:19,870
my first military campaign
with the late Emperor.

194
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:22,840
Don't you think we should celebrate?

195
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,280
Of course, we should.

196
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:25,550
Lord Zhang,

197
00:09:25,870 --> 00:09:28,480
without the battles you
and the late Emperor fought,

198
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:30,360
Jinglan wouldn't be what it is today.

199
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:30,870
Yes.

200
00:09:30,870 --> 00:09:32,670
Come on. Let me offer you a toast,
Lord Zhang.

201
00:09:32,670 --> 00:09:33,750
To Your Majesty.

202
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:34,870
Cheers.

203
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:44,480
He

204
00:09:44,910 --> 00:09:45,960
left again.

205
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:48,360
He said he would come back.

206
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,270
I highly doubt it.

207
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:53,630
I saw Lord Zhang at the door earlier

208
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:54,750
with a lot of wine.

209
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:57,240
I don't know what he's up to tonight.

210
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:00,490
I will wait for him anyway.

211
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,150
Alright.

212
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,180
Then, I'll accompany you.

213
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:17,150
Come on.

214
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,280
Let me fill your cup, Lord Zhang.

215
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:22,510
Back then,

216
00:10:22,910 --> 00:10:24,480
I followed the late Emperor

217
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:27,790
and fought our way
through the battlefields.

218
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,720
I deeply understand

219
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:32,000
how hard-won this empire is.

220
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:36,880
The late Emperor passed away suddenly

221
00:10:37,270 --> 00:10:39,400
and asked me to be your Chief Minister.

222
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,440
Actually, Your Majesty,

223
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:46,600
at my age,

224
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,440
I should have retired long ago

225
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,670
and enjoyed my twilight years.

226
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:51,750
To be honest,

227
00:10:51,910 --> 00:10:55,150
I should have lived a carefree
life with my grandchildren.

228
00:10:55,150 --> 00:10:57,240
Really, Lord Zhang?

229
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,170
With this glass,

230
00:10:58,670 --> 00:11:00,120
I wish you

231
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:02,320
many children and grandchildren.

232
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,760
Thank you, Your Majesty.

233
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:06,080
After you, Lord Zhang.

234
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:06,750
Please.

235
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:07,840
Your Majesty.

236
00:11:11,030 --> 00:11:13,490
You can really hold your liquor,
Lord Zhang.

237
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,550
Your Majesty,

238
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:20,200
I am truly not clinging to

239
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:22,630
the position of Chief Minister.

240
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:26,840
I just worry about you, Your Majesty.

241
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,120
I also worry about

242
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:31,150
Jinglan's land

243
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,030
Lord Zhang.

244
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:33,240
and its people.

245
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:35,390
I cannot do it without you.

246
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,390
Jinglan

247
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:38,080
needs you even more.

248
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,150
Lord Zhang.

249
00:11:39,150 --> 00:11:40,810
You flatter me, Your Majesty.

250
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:43,320
You flatter me, Your Majesty.

251
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:43,960
Come on.

252
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:52,790
Your Majesty,

253
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:55,030
I invited you out tonight

254
00:11:55,270 --> 00:11:57,600
not only to commemorate the late Emperor,

255
00:11:57,670 --> 00:12:00,120
but also because I don't want you

256
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:03,030
to lose yourself
in Consort Ling's tenderness

257
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:06,080
and be unable to extricate yourself.

258
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:08,670
Rest assured.

259
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:11,120
I will definitely be

260
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:14,750
a wise ruler who knows
how to judge and use people.

261
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,030
Good, Your Majesty.

262
00:12:20,030 --> 00:12:23,360
Remember to cherish this hard-won empire

263
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:25,440
and the people of Jinglan.

264
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,600
I believe

265
00:12:27,910 --> 00:12:30,510
you will certainly be
a wise and just emperor.

266
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:31,600
To Your Majesty.

267
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,630
Then, with this cup,

268
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:34,600
we toast to the land of Jinglan,

269
00:12:34,750 --> 00:12:36,240
and to the future of Jinglan.

270
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,120
Lord Zhang.

271
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,030
Please.

272
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,080
Your Majesty.

273
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,670
Your Majesty.

274
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:11,150
It is all for Jinglan.

275
00:13:32,750 --> 00:13:34,670
Judging by the Your Highness's look,

276
00:13:34,670 --> 00:13:36,480
the treasury must be full again.

277
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:38,390
The weather has been good,

278
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:39,790
and the land is peaceful this year.

279
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:42,200
Both the national and royal treasuries

280
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:44,260
have 30% more than in previous years.

281
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:46,440
This is truly worth celebrating.

282
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:47,790
However,

283
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:50,220
this is all thanks to you, Your Highness.

284
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:53,120
I heard

285
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:55,360
that His Majesty spent the most
on his royal wedding

286
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,390
compared to all previous monarchs.

287
00:13:58,750 --> 00:14:00,440
I only have one brother.

288
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,870
It's his first marriage.

289
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:03,080
As his sister,

290
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,360
how could I be stingy?

291
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:06,670
You are so good to His Majesty,
Your Highness.

292
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:08,360
I hope His Majesty will always keep

293
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,890
this kindness in his heart.

294
00:14:12,390 --> 00:14:13,550
I heard that

295
00:14:13,550 --> 00:14:17,750
His Majesty and Consort Ling didn't
consummate their marriage last night.

296
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,320
Lord Zhang

297
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,780
is such a stubborn old man.

298
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:22,270
The ceremony is only complete

299
00:14:22,270 --> 00:14:24,030
after the marriage is consummated.

300
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:25,120
Why is he

301
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,250
standing in the way?

302
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:29,870
Should we help His Majesty out?

303
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:31,390
No.

304
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,480
It's their own business.

305
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:34,010
Let nature take its course.

306
00:14:37,150 --> 00:14:37,750
By the way,

307
00:14:38,390 --> 00:14:40,390
did Consort Ling say anything?

308
00:14:40,390 --> 00:14:42,150
Consort Ling is fine.

309
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,750
But Jin Xi,

310
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,870
the female official beside her,

311
00:14:47,870 --> 00:14:49,330
is indeed a hidden danger.

312
00:14:50,030 --> 00:14:51,630
We can't let her stay in the palace.

313
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:53,290
Find a chance to drive her out.

314
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:55,000
Go prepare a courtyard.

315
00:14:55,870 --> 00:14:57,150
The palace

316
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:59,480
must be clean.

317
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:07,910
Don't you think

318
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,980
Chu has something on his mind?

319
00:15:10,790 --> 00:15:12,440
General Xiao, you are so clever.

320
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:14,170
Why don't you ask him yourself?

321
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:15,790
Chu...

322
00:15:16,790 --> 00:15:17,790
Don't ask.

323
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:19,960
I'm fine.

324
00:15:21,270 --> 00:15:22,120
I'm good.

325
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:23,720
Chu,

326
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:25,790
it seems that since the marriage alliance,

327
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:27,390
you haven't been very happy.

328
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:30,030
I am quite happy.

329
00:15:30,550 --> 00:15:33,120
Then, why do you look so exhausted?

330
00:15:36,030 --> 00:15:37,080
Chu,

331
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:39,030
are you and Consort Ling

332
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:41,790
not sleeping well?

333
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:44,360
What kind of question is that?

334
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:47,180
It's mostly Zhang Ruizhong's fault.

335
00:15:47,790 --> 00:15:48,630
Lord Zhang,

336
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:50,870
that stubborn old man,

337
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,150
every night,

338
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:54,000
when Wanyu and I are together,

339
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:56,480
he insists on eavesdropping at our door.

340
00:15:56,550 --> 00:15:58,120
He either wants to discuss

341
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,150
national affairs with me,

342
00:15:59,150 --> 00:16:01,880
or wants to drink
and have a heart-to-heart talk.

343
00:16:02,670 --> 00:16:04,070
He is a veteran minister.

344
00:16:04,550 --> 00:16:06,410
It's inappropriate if I don't go.

345
00:16:06,550 --> 00:16:07,950
But I can't outdrink him.

346
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:11,140
I really don't know what to do.

347
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:14,880
General Xiao,

348
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,960
can you tolerate this?

349
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:18,360
I cannot.

350
00:16:18,550 --> 00:16:19,480
Lord Fei,

351
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:20,670
can you?

352
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:21,870
I can't either.

353
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:24,550
Do you have a solution, General Xiao?

354
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:26,270
That depends on what solution

355
00:16:26,270 --> 00:16:27,750
Lord Fei has.

356
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:29,480
What are you two talking about?

357
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:30,550
Chu,

358
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:32,480
rest assured.

359
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:35,360
Tonight, we'll let you and Consort Ling...

360
00:16:40,670 --> 00:16:42,000
We shall take our leave.

361
00:16:42,030 --> 00:16:43,160
Where are you going?

362
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:44,200
Wait.

363
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:45,390
Tell me.

364
00:16:45,390 --> 00:16:46,440
Tell me where you are going.

365
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,570
Where are you going?

366
00:16:49,870 --> 00:16:50,670
Jin Xi.

367
00:16:51,510 --> 00:16:53,640
Did you pick all these from the palace?

368
00:16:53,670 --> 00:16:54,440
Yes.

369
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,480
I took one branch from every tree,

370
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:58,480
and three blooms from every flower,

371
00:16:58,600 --> 00:16:59,750
and got this many.

372
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:01,670
You just came to the palace.

373
00:17:01,670 --> 00:17:03,870
Why are you so familiar with the palace?

374
00:17:05,790 --> 00:17:06,790
Not really.

375
00:17:08,589 --> 00:17:10,119
Greetings, Your Highness.

376
00:17:13,589 --> 00:17:14,750
Greetings, Xie.

377
00:17:15,109 --> 00:17:15,960
You may rise.

378
00:17:16,240 --> 00:17:17,880
Xie, what brings you here?

379
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:19,200
I came to see you.

380
00:17:20,069 --> 00:17:20,790
How is it?

381
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:23,700
Are you getting used to
living in the palace?

382
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:25,680
I eat well in the palace,

383
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,540
and sleep well.

384
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:27,960
I am doing very well.

385
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:28,720
Good？

386
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:34,130
I heard you and His Mahesty
haven't consummated your marriage yet.

387
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:39,640
Liu Chu has been a bit busy lately.

388
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,550
Good things take time.

389
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:44,880
You two will be together for a lifetime,

390
00:17:45,030 --> 00:17:46,480
so there's no rush.

391
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:47,800
Rest assured.

392
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:48,960
With me here,

393
00:17:49,030 --> 00:17:50,510
you will

394
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:51,640
have a happy life.

395
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,440
I came today

396
00:17:58,030 --> 00:18:00,350
mainly to talk to you about Jin Xi.

397
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:03,030
Jin Xi?

398
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:04,790
I heard

399
00:18:04,790 --> 00:18:06,960
Jin Xi is very loyal to you.

400
00:18:07,350 --> 00:18:09,480
She accompanied you
from Changmo to Jinglan,

401
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,610
and into the palace.

402
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:12,830
Now that you are with His Majesty,

403
00:18:12,830 --> 00:18:14,000
I'm thinking of

404
00:18:14,030 --> 00:18:15,830
finding a good home for her.

405
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,640
Outside the palace,

406
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:20,880
I have a courtyard.

407
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,530
I plan to let her live there.

408
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:23,960
And every month,

409
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:27,240
I'll allocate some money from the treasury
for her living expenses.

410
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,240
But

411
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:30,440
Jin Xi and I are like sisters.

412
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:31,810
If she is not here...

413
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:35,070
Precisely because you are like sisters,

414
00:18:35,070 --> 00:18:36,480
she shouldn't stay by your side forever

415
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,590
to serve you.

416
00:18:38,030 --> 00:18:39,640
She needs her own residence,

417
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:40,640
her own life,

418
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,770
and her own husband.

419
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:43,880
Don't you agree?

420
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:51,540
Your Highness's good intentions

421
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:52,960
are surely meant well.

422
00:18:53,270 --> 00:18:54,590
Since you've said so,

423
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:56,850
there must be no chance for negotiation.

424
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:58,140
I can leave the palace.

425
00:18:58,400 --> 00:18:59,880
But after I leave,

426
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:02,740
who can take care of Her Highness?

427
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,270
Rest assured about that.

428
00:19:04,270 --> 00:19:04,920
I will arrange for

429
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:07,160
more clever maids to serve you.

430
00:19:07,480 --> 00:19:08,440
As long as I have time,

431
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:09,640
I will also come see you.

432
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:10,480
Besides,

433
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:12,750
you're not forbidden from
entering the palace forever.

434
00:19:12,750 --> 00:19:14,400
Whenever you miss Consort Ling,

435
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:16,000
you can come see her anytime.

436
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:19,590
Okay.

437
00:19:19,790 --> 00:19:21,030
Then, I am relieved.

438
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:24,730
I will follow Your Highness's
arrangements.

439
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:26,920
Then,

440
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,550
it's settled?

441
00:19:30,270 --> 00:19:31,070
Okay.

442
00:19:48,790 --> 00:19:49,270
Who is it?

443
00:19:49,270 --> 00:19:50,470
Keep your voice down.

444
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:51,840
Keep your voice down.

445
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:53,240
Lord Zhang
has been looking for me all night.

446
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,350
He's so annoying.

447
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,880
If Lord Zhang is looking for you, just go.

448
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:58,610
He has no real business with me.

449
00:19:58,640 --> 00:19:59,960
It's all nonsense.

450
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:01,700
Or he's just lecturing me.

451
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:03,880
I think

452
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:06,070
he just doesn't want me to come here.

453
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:09,480
But I'm not going anywhere today.

454
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:16,270
Your Majesty,
I've been waiting for you for a long time.

455
00:20:16,270 --> 00:20:17,400
Let me deal with him.

456
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:18,720
Your Majesty.

457
00:20:19,070 --> 00:20:20,030
Lord Zhang.

458
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:21,400
Why are you here?

459
00:20:21,590 --> 00:20:24,750
I have something to discuss
with His Majesty.

460
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:30,270
Backup is here.

461
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:31,110
Lord Zhang.

462
00:20:31,310 --> 00:20:33,000
You brought so much good wine.

463
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,590
General Xiao and I are just about to
have a drink together.

464
00:20:35,590 --> 00:20:36,200
Why don't we go together?

465
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:38,550
No. No. I really have business
with His Majesty.

466
00:20:38,550 --> 00:20:39,400
Lord Zhang, come on.

467
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:41,880
Let me tell you something interesting
about the Tianlang Pass.

468
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:42,240
No.

469
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:42,830
The wine...

470
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:43,750
Let's go, Lord Zhang.

471
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:45,200
I want to drink with His Majesty.

472
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:46,240
What's the point of drinking here?

473
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:47,310
Let's drink at Tianxiang Restaurant.

474
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:49,570
I really have business with His Majesty.

475
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:53,800
They won't come back, will they?

476
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:54,880
They won't.

477
00:20:55,270 --> 00:20:57,350
Although Xiao Chi can't hold his drink,

478
00:20:57,350 --> 00:20:59,720
Fei Zheng can hold his liquor.

479
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:00,550
Huh？

480
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:02,000
What's up?

481
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:04,110
Anyway, tonight,

482
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:05,770
I'm not going anywhere.

483
00:21:06,270 --> 00:21:07,160
Your Majesty.

484
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:11,240
Who is it?

485
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:12,070
Your Majesty,

486
00:21:12,270 --> 00:21:14,790
Her Highness sent nuptial wine.

487
00:21:14,790 --> 00:21:16,350
Thank you, Xie.

488
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:17,880
Can you leave it at the door?

489
00:21:32,270 --> 00:21:34,030
Go out and have a drink.

490
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,590
Drink again?

491
00:21:36,750 --> 00:21:37,640
Drink what?

492
00:22:21,350 --> 00:22:22,480
Your Majesty.

493
00:22:26,400 --> 00:22:27,640
Your Majesty.

494
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:31,270
Stop shouting.

495
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:35,240
But we have to attend the morning court.

496
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:42,110
Wait for me.

497
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,740
I will accompany you after the court.

498
00:23:04,270 --> 00:23:06,310
His Majesty has arrived.

499
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:07,480
Your Majesty.

500
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:09,510
At ease.

501
00:23:09,750 --> 00:23:10,720
Rise.

502
00:23:12,750 --> 00:23:14,010
Is she still sleeping?

503
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:15,030
Yes.

504
00:23:49,640 --> 00:23:51,440
Your Majesty, why are you here?

505
00:23:51,750 --> 00:23:53,480
Jin Xi, why didn't you tell me?

506
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:54,940
I did it on purpose.

507
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:56,640
I told them not to wake you.

508
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:59,240
I just wanted to see you sleep.

509
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:00,480
So cute.

510
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:02,160
I haven't washed up yet.

511
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:04,480
Then,

512
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:08,440
get up and wash up now.

513
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:09,400
Then,

514
00:24:09,790 --> 00:24:11,190
I'll take you somewhere.

515
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:12,830
Then, wait for me.

516
00:24:13,830 --> 00:24:14,350
Okay.

517
00:24:14,550 --> 00:24:16,030
I'll wait for you outside.

518
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:18,350
Sorry to keep Your Majesty waiting.

519
00:24:18,350 --> 00:24:19,880
Please wait for me outside.

520
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:20,680
Okay.

521
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,680
Why haven't you left yet?

522
00:24:31,030 --> 00:24:32,350
Hurry up and get out.

523
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:33,160
Get out.

524
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,240
I don't want to.

525
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,550
I don't want to go out.

526
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,570
It's daytime right now.

527
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:45,790
So what?

528
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,400
I don't care.

529
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:50,790
But I need to wash up.

530
00:24:51,030 --> 00:24:51,830
Okay.

531
00:24:52,350 --> 00:24:53,550
But I think

532
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:56,090
you look beautiful no matter what.

533
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:58,770
Aren't you going to take me out to play?

534
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:01,920
Yes.

535
00:25:02,350 --> 00:25:03,350
Then.

536
00:25:04,510 --> 00:25:06,070
I'll let you off today.

537
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:07,030
Thanks.

538
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:09,590
Then, I'll wait for you outside.

539
00:25:09,590 --> 00:25:10,160
Okay.

540
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:11,880
Hurry up and wash up.

541
00:25:13,110 --> 00:25:13,680
I'm waiting for you.

542
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:14,110
Okay.

543
00:26:06,070 --> 00:26:08,270
Jinglan has a vast territory.

544
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:10,750
It has nine provinces
and eighteen counties.

545
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:11,960
It faces the sea to the east,

546
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,480
has grasslands to the west,

547
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:15,480
and borders Mount Jing to the south.

548
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,160
To the north

549
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:17,880
is your Changmo.

550
00:26:18,590 --> 00:26:21,480
If Changmo and Jinglan can
maintain good relations for generations,

551
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,720
then the whole world

552
00:26:23,200 --> 00:26:24,600
will be at peace forever.

553
00:26:25,590 --> 00:26:26,590
The King of Changmo has already sent you

554
00:26:26,590 --> 00:26:28,030
to Jinglan as a hostage.

555
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:29,880
How could the two countries

556
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:31,480
not be on good terms forever?

557
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:33,080
I came here voluntarily.

558
00:26:34,550 --> 00:26:35,750
All right.

559
00:26:36,640 --> 00:26:37,350
I swear,

560
00:26:37,750 --> 00:26:38,880
from now on,

561
00:26:39,030 --> 00:26:39,750
Jinglan

562
00:26:39,750 --> 00:26:40,510
and Changmo

563
00:26:41,270 --> 00:26:42,600
will be like one family,

564
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,350
and there will be no more wars.

565
00:26:44,350 --> 00:26:45,440
I will also

566
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:46,960
teach our children

567
00:26:47,070 --> 00:26:49,240
and all the descendants of Jinglan

568
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:50,960
to keep this promise.

569
00:26:52,030 --> 00:26:52,880
Okay.

570
00:26:59,350 --> 00:27:00,310
You have sent many spies

571
00:27:00,310 --> 00:27:01,830
in the past years.

572
00:27:02,030 --> 00:27:03,310
Now, your Caidie Hall

573
00:27:03,310 --> 00:27:05,030
is finally being useful, huh?

574
00:27:06,270 --> 00:27:08,790
Jinglan's national strength is
stronger than Changmo's.

575
00:27:08,790 --> 00:27:10,120
They have more talents.

576
00:27:10,270 --> 00:27:12,350
Many members of our Caidie Hall died.

577
00:27:12,350 --> 00:27:14,950
Finally, we managed to
plant a few spies there.

578
00:27:15,030 --> 00:27:16,110
General Gan,

579
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:18,330
didn't you fail to defeat Xiao Chi?

580
00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:20,400
On the battlefield,

581
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:23,160
there aren't many
who can fight me for a few rounds.

582
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,000
Let alone

583
00:27:24,070 --> 00:27:25,550
fight me to a draw.

584
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:28,200
As they say, heroes appreciate heroes.

585
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,270
Besides,

586
00:27:29,480 --> 00:27:30,550
I didn't kill him

587
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:33,030
because I wanted to play a little longer.

588
00:27:33,030 --> 00:27:35,070
Then, be careful, General Gan.

589
00:27:35,350 --> 00:27:37,480
Don't risk your life.

590
00:27:37,790 --> 00:27:38,270
You!

591
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:47,420
Greetings, Your Majesty.

592
00:27:50,270 --> 00:27:52,590
This marriage alliance went smoothly.

593
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:56,080
Caidie Hall made a great contribution.

594
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,590
Thank you, Your Majesty.

595
00:27:57,590 --> 00:27:58,270
Rise.

596
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,680
I'm thinking that

597
00:28:01,750 --> 00:28:02,510
Fei Zheng

598
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:04,200
has been in Jinglan for years.

599
00:28:04,200 --> 00:28:05,590
It's time he made himself useful.

600
00:28:05,590 --> 00:28:06,200
Yes.

601
00:28:06,400 --> 00:28:09,000
I will go to Jinglan
with the marriage alliance envoy.

602
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:11,000
I will officially activate him then.

603
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:11,800
Your Majesty,

604
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:13,680
we don't need to
go through all that trouble.

605
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,920
Just attack Jinglan directly.

606
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,070
Wouldn't that be more satisfying?

607
00:28:16,070 --> 00:28:18,030
Tianlang Pass is
a key stronghold of Jinglan.

608
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:19,440
It is easy to defend and hard to attack.

609
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:21,640
General Gan,
you only want the thrill of the kill,

610
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:24,750
completely ignoring
the lives of our Changmo soldiers, huh?

611
00:28:24,750 --> 00:28:25,640
Using venomous insects and poison

612
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:26,880
is despicable.

613
00:28:27,030 --> 00:28:28,240
Even if we win,

614
00:28:28,240 --> 00:28:29,840
it will be an unfair victory.

615
00:28:30,350 --> 00:28:31,270
Whatever methods are used

616
00:28:31,270 --> 00:28:32,350
or schemes are played,

617
00:28:32,350 --> 00:28:33,750
they are all reasonable.

618
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:35,160
General Gan,

619
00:28:35,270 --> 00:28:36,480
do you think a war between two countries

620
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:38,350
is just a fight between two kids?

621
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:40,270
Do you know

622
00:28:40,270 --> 00:28:41,030
how many soldiers
will die in the flames of war?

623
00:28:41,030 --> 00:28:42,000
Victory

624
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,460
is the most important.

625
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,590
Well said, Military Advisor Modu.

626
00:28:48,590 --> 00:28:50,640
We must win with the lowest cost

627
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:53,200
and the most secure method.

628
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:56,790
Gan Yi, continue training the troops.

629
00:28:56,790 --> 00:28:57,590
Rest assured.

630
00:28:57,680 --> 00:28:59,550
There will be a time for you
to fulfill your ambitions.

631
00:28:59,550 --> 00:29:00,610
I accept the order.

632
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:03,200
Military Advisor Modu,

633
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:03,880
next time,

634
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:07,750
you should go to Jinglan
with the tribute envoy.

635
00:29:07,750 --> 00:29:08,240
Yes.

636
00:29:09,310 --> 00:29:10,920
I have already prepared

637
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:12,350
a surprise for Liu Chu.

638
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:14,960
As for you...

639
00:29:17,030 --> 00:29:18,640
I know what I need to do.

640
00:29:21,160 --> 00:29:21,680
Good.

641
00:29:22,680 --> 00:29:23,590
Excellent.

642
00:29:40,880 --> 00:29:41,790
Liu Zheng.

643
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:44,480
The day I conquer Jinglan,

644
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:47,030
in front of your grave,

645
00:29:47,790 --> 00:29:50,480
I will kill your son, Liu Chu,

646
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:53,480
to keep you company.
